&lt;/h2>&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/@hugo-fixit/fixit-releaser"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">&lt;img loading="lazy" src='https://img.shields.io/npm/v/@hugo-fixit/fixit-releaser.svg' alt="NPM version">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>中文 | &lt;a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hugo-fixit/fixit-releaser/refs/heads/main/README.en.md"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">English&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>版本控制、变更日志和发布工具，支持 Conventional Commits 规范。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="功能">&lt;span>功能&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e5%8a%9f%e8%83%bd" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>更新 FixIt 内部版本号。(&lt;strong>仅适用于 &lt;a href="https://github.com/hugo-fixit/FixIt"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">FixIt&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a>&lt;/strong>)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>根据 &lt;a href="https://www.conventionalcommits.org/zh-hans/v1.0.0/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Conventional Commits&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a> 规范自动生成变更日志
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>feat:&lt;/code> 新功能&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>fix:&lt;/code> 修复问题&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>docs:&lt;/code> 文档变更&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>style:&lt;/code> 代码格式调整&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>refactor:&lt;/code> 代码重构&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>perf:&lt;/code> 性能优化&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>test:&lt;/code> 测试相关&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>chore:&lt;/code> 构建过程或辅助工具的变动&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>revert:&lt;/code> 代码回滚&lt;/li>
&lt;li>支持 scope：&lt;code>feat(api):&lt;/code>, &lt;code>fix(ui):&lt;/code> 等&lt;/li>
&lt;li>支持 emoji：&lt;code>:sparkles: feat:&lt;/code>, &lt;code>✨ feat:&lt;/code> 等&lt;/li>
&lt;li>支持 Breaking Changes：&lt;code>feat!:&lt;/code>, &lt;code>feat(scope)!:&lt;/code>, &lt;code>BREAKING CHANGE:&lt;/code> 等格式&lt;/li>
&lt;li>自动忽略 WIP 提交：&lt;code>wip:&lt;/code>, &lt;code>Wip:&lt;/code> 等临时提交不会包含在变更日志中&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
